  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA93">
<l>avaṉkaṇṭāy vāṉōr pirāṉāvā ṉeṉṟu</l>
<l>mavaṉkaṇṭā yampavaḷa vaṇṇa - ṉavaṉkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>maittamarnta kaṇṭattāṉ maṟṟavaṉpā ṉaṉṉeñcē</l>
<l>meyttamarntaṉ pāynī virumpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He, see, always is the lord of the celestials.</l>
<l>He, see, is of pretty coral colour. He, see,</l>
<l>is the one in whose throat something black abides. In him again, good heart,</l>
<l>dwell bodily, you, being love, [and] long [for him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
